{"tid":2410284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昂山素姬被控第二項罪名 違反天然災害管理法","createTime":"2021-02-16T12:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T13:02:24.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"30f26fe3759984f003716f130707109af016f493","tid":2410284,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:55:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3440794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3440794&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=e83d7ab8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3440794&h=af8ec4da\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3440794</a><br />\n<br />\n〔中央社〕翁山蘇姬（Aung San Suu Kyi）的律師金蒙紹（Khin Maung Zaw）今天表示，緬甸軍事政權對遭罷黜領袖翁山蘇姬提出第二項指控，這次是違反國家天然災害管理法。<br />\n<br />\n金蒙紹告訴法新社，當局又指控翁山蘇姬違反天然災害管理法。<br />\n<br />\n自翁山蘇姬遭罷黜後，已因家中遭查獲非法持有無線電對講機，被控違反國家進出口法。<br />\n<br />\n詢及她的健康狀態時，金蒙紹表示「沒消息就是好消息。我們還沒接獲任何壞消息。」<br />\n<br />\n他說，下一次開庭審理日期為3月1日。<br />\n<br />\n國家領導委員會發言人紹敏通（Zaw Min Tun）准將在記者會上表示：「我們的目標是舉行選舉，並將權力移交給勝選政黨。」這是軍方1日發動政變以來首次召開記者會。<br />\n<br />\n軍方尚未公布選舉的確切日期，但已宣布全國進入緊急狀態為期一年。"},{"pid":"df12dcaf98325143a4bc3d13d599c000d6f65078","tid":2410284,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.yupoo.com/wwlb/BrLM6DOE/uQRwh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.yupoo.com%2Fwwlb%2FBrLM6DOE%2FuQRwh.jpg&h=596263ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"742d89adbb96b05150bb189fda00da1e3ebab8aa","tid":2410284,"uid":37546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:57:35.000Z","msg":"即係乜撚嘢？"},{"pid":"5bb0ea45c7493ee84bcc1f54f0777f08b9f18b49","tid":2410284,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" 